    "A survey was conducted in Blekinge Tekniska Högskola, Sweden, involving learners and educators experienced with V Labs in their courses.",
    "The response rates were 29% for the learners and 73% for the educators, the survey results indicating a positive perception of V Labs in enhancing AL in cybersecurity education.",
    "The findings highlight that V Labs are considered engaging, interactive, and effective in fostering a better understanding of cybersecurity concepts, emphasizing their role in improving AL and problemsolving skills in remote education settings.",
